data.description: Situated in the charming Walnut Grove community, nestled in the heart of downtown Pendergrass, this residence boasts an array of amenities, including a pool, clubhouse, and playground. Ideally positioned between Athens and Gainesville, with easy access to I-85 and Hwy 129, this property offers both convenience and comfort. Step into the inviting entry foyer of this highly coveted Hanover floor plan home, which seamlessly leads to a spacious family room. The open kitchen is adorned with granite countertops, pristine white cabinets, stainless-steel appliances, and a generously sized island, making it an ideal space for culinary pursuits. A bedroom on the main floor with a full bath adds to the home's practicality. Upstairs, a loft area provides additional flexibility and space. The oversized primary suite is a luxurious retreat, featuring a dual vanity, soaker tub, separate shower, and a walk-in closet. The residence also includes generously proportioned secondary bedrooms, ensuring ample space for family and guests. Completing the picture is a delightful rocking chair front porch, offering a perfect spot to unwind and enjoy the picturesque surroundings. With its thoughtful design, convenient location, and attractive features, this property epitomizes the ideal home in Walnut Grove.
